---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import DefaultLayout from '../layouts/Default.astro';
import PageTitle from '~/components/shared/PageTitle.astro';
import IconWave from '~/assets/icons/wave.svg';
---

<DefaultLayout title="Bruno Paz | About me">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <Image
        src={IconWave}
        height="80"
        width="80"
        class="mx-auto mb-6 opacity-90 animate-wave"
        alt="Hi There!"
        title="Hi there!"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <PageTitle title="About me" />
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-neutral-800">Hey, there!</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          My name is Bruno Paz, and I am a Tech Lead / Software Engineer from Porto, Portugal ðŸ‡µðŸ‡¹, with <strong>
            10+ years of experience
          </strong> building web applications and <strong>3+ years of experience</strong> leading engineering teams, across
          diverse sectors including <strong>E-Commerce</strong>, <strong>Travel</strong>, <strong>Payments</strong>, and <strong
          >
            Healthcare
          </strong>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          As a Software Engineer, I specialize in <strong>Backend Development</strong>, currently working primarily with <strong
          >
            Golang
          </strong>, <strong>TypeScript</strong> and <strong>Node.js.</strong>
          I've also have past experience with <strong>PHP/Symfony</strong> and
          <strong>Java</strong>, having built production systems with all these technologies.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          As a <strong>Tech Lead</strong>, I focus on bridging technical execution with team growth. I guide
          architectural decisions, mentor engineers, and establish practices that help teams deliver quality software. I
          believe in leading by example and build a culture of trust, collaboration and transparency.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-neutral-800">What Drives Me</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I'm deeply passionate about technology and its potential to solve real-world problems. My interests span
          multiple areas from <strong>Backend Development</strong>, <strong>Systems Design</strong>,
          <strong>DevOps & Automation</strong>, and emerging technologies that enable a more decentralized and open web.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          As a <strong>lifelong learner</strong>, I'm continuously driven by curiosity, always seeking new challenges
          and opportunities to expand my knowledge and refine my skills.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I strongly believe in <strong>using technology as a force for good</strong>, building solutions that improve
          people's lives and contribute to a better world.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-neutral-800">Beyond the Code</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          While technology is a significant part of my life, I believe in maintaining balance. Outside of work, I enjoy <strong
          >
            sports
          </strong>, <strong>watching TV series and anime</strong>, and <strong>
            spending quality time with friends over dinner
          </strong>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-neutral-800">Open Source & Community</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I'm an active contributor to the open-source community, creating tools and libraries that help developers work
          more efficiently. You can find my projects on
          <a
            href="https://github.com/brpaz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I also share my knowledge and experiences through
          <a href="/blog/page/1" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline">my blog</a>, covering
          multiple tech related topics.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-neutral-800">Let's Connect</h2>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers, discussing technology, or exploring potential
          collaboration opportunities. Feel free to reach out through
          <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline">the contact page</a>
          or connect with me on
          <a
            href="https://github.com/brpaz"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 underline"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</DefaultLayout>

<style>
  @keyframes wave {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    25% {
      transform: rotate(20deg);
    }
    75% {
      transform: rotate(-20deg);
    }
  }

  .animate-wave {
    animation: wave 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
